import JSEncrypt from "jsencrypt"

// http://web.chacuo.net/netrsakeypair 000216

const publicKey = "MFwwDQYJKoZIhvcNAQEBBQADSwAwSAJBALqt37mGMQtxKZ5Oq3h9hFRJIKDt3GpR\n"+
"XEyqC69kS3S86G7vragpP9EPE9zQrtb1nYIdqhOGxkL8u0+X77JFj4MCAwEAAQ=="

const privateKey = "MIIFDjBABgkqhkiG9w0BBQ0wMzAbBgkqhkiG9w0BBQwwDgQIzyWuHm/Dda8CAggA/n"+
"MBQGCCqGSIb3DQMHBAgqdZSsCOPebwSCBMgqQD3ORAsguKJryVSZISCN2GTiEDAP\n"+
"4TNST0GyYETf7wfwq5leG69JhGVm/m6ClL2QV8nN97df63pvKH7Ko9a+zkcEFZ5W\n"+
"FkLOz7lAzi5XaVDHLLuYSzELN5lBwCPTB5VMUK8lD75shad3mzjqO1vhmkhvJA/8\n"+
"2w54bYnQ3ZnzgS4+/hngeQ7cMLSYQgaQDd2gJ6ALmo5cy1QiXDJrXwIRePVb/nGa\n"+
"OIXo/5MZPBWDRiSsEV2tMcQvsTmywMrJw0ABomn1Vk44wFEQy99+Sy+I2vIp7yvC\n"+
"SrJIyLGPYAMevJo+e91INpWDjvwlhHz3GscbEzKzRJfIYIseu0ec4QxIw4qcP3Ae\n"+
"5jV7txf0axWrPMd3B9WipaJpe62qSAwy9Y8u43E0Fog868k+x10P447ybodwv46N\n"+
"RW1ztXWKOBrqsmNe6Q9YbCUN1iio0wylg5HDoLt8ZbsNFoBv7S/FJstl87/Dhz3y\n"+
"iJ0Vi9sqbg7Z4Frexv2VGcoX0aH0Fq9uYCP7Drg3WYqqMUbWWaZPSoh6B55puaBw\n"+
"0uKFAfPpqLWVPefbEH45G3Agul+qcopPRG4DkkmExEAUEoq47TxqUhVZYfiLID+g\n"+
"q4S6Txvj8LKEa4dMQ68t1lHq/Ckz1ZGDLasiAeBMOYvyczhjEB5y6ozH8NKwJa/S\n"+
"QPuqyNQTTvdmvdQJwHlS/sdOgeIl54QxjpsgSFsN8IPW1MZCnAxu88nsfnNcfBya\n"+
"lDu87lcO19OReMh6FP8+wHuxcj9DB2l2lcbXgqexFg17OHAp6+VC0jYGaH9+zfpC\n"+
"NAUwYCASDMmgw7UJGxAAZ945+Yu+ZEIWBRw/kR50myGjwfWj57Dbr+JDS4ffuAmq\n"+
"qmx8pfiQ09+h41kXL3owCUGCSHn5xbSw/9tuc4rg3cSRzwOkyrU1u2o/QITBcvgG\n"+
"zpSiqDDyFHnmrRoqPcPBmMqJFz0Qd2bTSQ3IX9q8p0B2FUIiNbmPPaAmndnjl6Fi\n"+
"5OrZq+6g86V1yclrhg4AvS8qtEBK3UvIE2FXcFDS4GFlbr443W72JeI0WSAz0YCa\n"+
"MYC/GiPJffOX6NWOagxtnX6Vsa63tC22PjOy2qt8vIJpIIv5+bxGwkSTm1fg/EdL\n"+
"IP32XhvCq9JRmxw1OHmeE0WY1RBulFKn1ybaytuccgJVXD9kVzT4L/8zMA5Tkh2F\n"+
"55byNQV11dX4pS+iso2htB9deDuNDnBx1eOLizax2838c/ffEN7rGOB4wd/o2OZX\n"+
"ySGWpHfq611zfQTMLVaSZS2MRtWJk8jwMOL4udPLS/Ra/yhpFE6/P3ibQx29WeYg\n"+
"PIMnTZn2MKIlezKw336mSXOtn4ou2paTHhzFc2n2UlNkCsQ37AqyXTqrBSnZKGGr\n"+
"rNXt0yQvXl29vwi3Bi2zxM97P9uX6eLKMRFRWVEgiRY4TdmpMPenw5zb93Or4dzQ\n"+
"I0Qqg+Mn+Jq6dEbBXd38EmykDF1f9CuuvU3zILRS7SucPy6STZQITUIX5iaihHCp\n"+
"iGo1gijpFznhP7ZREnIkl2Mu6x2imn8JQ/6hR07DGWdRcldz3nKH2/7jH34YmXNa\n"+
"I8/j0Nmd98hJ2A/U3PNpuxTKJx7gh7sR4kMJeKmADpxdLmVbMn4tXymewzujJXDu\n"+
"b78="

//加密
export function encrypt(txt) {
    const encryptor = new JSEncrypt()
    encryptor.setPublicKey(publicKey) //设置公钥
    return encryptor.encrypt(txt) //加密
}

//解密
export function decrypt(txt) {
    const encryptor = new JSEncrypt()
    encryptor.setPrivateKey(privateKey) //设置私钥
    return encryptor.decrypt(txt) //解密
}
